  <brief_title>How is Physical Activity Level and Educational Expectations of Patient With Knee Osteoarthritis : Epidemiological Study in Spa Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>How is Physical Activity Level and Educational Expectations of Patient With Knee Osteoarthritis : Epidemiological Study in Spa Therapy</official_title>
